                <h3 class="font-special font-semibold text-xl capitalize inline-flex items-center">
                    spoilers &nbsp;
                    <span class="det-icon text-gray-400 text-xs cursor-pointer">
                        <i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i>
                        (Show Spoilers)
                    </span> 
                    <span class="det-icon text-gray-400 text-xs cursor-pointer hidden">
                        <i class="fa fa-caret-up"></i>
                        (Hide Spoilers)
                    </span> 
